name: STATE v. Gerald GORDON et al.

parties: STATE v. Gerald GORDON et al.

opinions.text:
ORDER
The state’s motion to dismiss this appeal is assigned to the motion calendar for Wednesday, April 9, 1980 at 9:30 a. m. for oral argument. The clerk of the Superior Court is directed to file with this court those exhibits which were not transmitted with the record.

attorneys: Dennis J. Roberts II, Atty. Gen., Faith A. LaSalle, Special Asst. Atty. Gen., for plaintiff.
Aram K. Berberian, Warwick, for defendants.
